headline: Franklin Templeton Canada Announces Fee Reductions for Certain Funds
summary: Franklin Templeton Canada today announced fee reductions of up to 70 basis points across multiple series of mutual funds, reflecting its ongoing commitment to offering competitive fees and enhancing value for investors.
